                "subtype": "sidebar",
                "sidebar_type": "locations",
                "sidebar_heading": "Locations",
                "image": {
                    "type": "image",
                    "name": "Locations",
                    "image": "Sidebar_3_Locations.png"
                },
                "html": "Cu siths can be found wherever the barrier between the Material Plane and the First World is weak, particularly in the marshy highlands of Ustalav, where stories of the fey stretch back as far as memory. Superstitious townsfolk believe cu siths drag their prey back to the First World, where their victims\u2019 immortal souls fuse with the vital energy of that wild plane."
            }
        ],
